# Auto-deploy workflow

After making any code changes in this project:

1. Stage all changes: `git add -A`
2. Commit with a short descriptive message: `git commit -m "Brief description of change"`
3. Push: the post-commit hook runs automatically and pushes to origin (Vercel deploys on push)

Do not skip this step. If the user requests changes, commit and push when done unless they ask otherwise.
